    "We reported there are themes in which we did not find literature reviews even for the central theme of education, for example, the use of gamification to foster IT, understanding the impacts of gamified curriculums, and recompilation of best implementation practices to evaluate or implement gamification in education, among others.",
    "There are even more opportunities in peripherical themes such as citizen science research and adaptative or tailored gamification.",
